Definition: An e-girl is a girl found on the internet playing video games.

After a long day at work, there’s nothing quite like coming home to my cozy couch, transforming into a laid-back e-girl.
target: 在工作了一整天后，没有什么比回到家中舒适的沙发上，变身为一个悠闲的电子女孩更棒的了。

Definition: Unsleeping means not sleeping.

Please put a warning next time and censor the image as this is very upsetting and disturbing work of art you produced and it has caused me many nights of unsleeping and nightmares because of how horrifying this is.

Definition: Satiety is the feeling or state of being sated.

Overeating is a symptom of a low satiety per calorie food environment in which you simultaneously need to eat more calories in order to achieve nutritional homeostasis and you also want to eat more calories.
target: 过度饮食是低饱腹感每卡路里食物环境的一个症状，在这种环境中，你需要同时摄入更多的卡路里才能达到营养稳态，而且你也想摄入更多的卡路里。

source: Overeating is a symptom of a low fat per calorie food environment in which you simultaneously need to eat more calories in order to achieve nutritional homeostasis and you also want to eat more calories.
target: 过度饮食是低脂肪热量食物环境的一种症状，在这种环境中，你需要同时摄入更多的热量以达到营养平衡，而且你也想摄入更多的热量。
